{
 "name": "RPlog_Small_Depot_Defense",
 "title": "Small Depot Defense",
 "summary": "A New Republic raiding force ambushes a lightly defended Imperial fuel depot guarded by Flight Officer Liza 'Slush' Molokai's bombers and TIE fighters, including the allergy-plagued Sub-Lieutenant Ricoar. Lance 'Wildman' Corbet leads the Republic strike alongside the mercenary Gren Delede in his Z-95 and his Marauder cruiser Eternal Vigilance, captained by Xar'on, while Razor Squadron's Dante and the pilot Raxis 'Raptor' L'ygr trade fire and trash-talk with the Imperials. The Republic punches through to seize a fuel container as the Imperial strike cruiser HIMS Broadsword microjumps in with reinforcements led by the Marshal Krieg, whose TIE is crippled but cunningly survives a torpedo hit. With their cargo secured and Vigilance away, the Republic pilots disengage and jump out, leaving the battered Imperials regrouping in defeat.",
